ActPilotage Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Transport of VERED KAMINKER of Toronto, Ontario, to be a member of the Great Lakes Pilotage Authority, to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Michael Pratt, whose term has expired.
